import React from 'react' import { Card, CardContent, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'; export default function Overview() { const classes = { marginBottom: '2%' } return ( Personality Overview

I've always resonated with the quote by Socrates - "The unexamined life is not worth living". For me, examining life translates into a deep desire to understand myself and the world around me. Fortunately, it became much easier for me to pursue such desires once I discovered the benefits and the power that personality frameworks could provide. What these frameworks allowed me to do was to understand my cognative functions and processes, my natural tendencies and default modes when processing and percieving reality, and I have also begun to understand how and why certain ideas ,environments ,people , and are more appealing to me than other. I enjoy the thrill of understanding, questioning, connecting and experiencing the wonders that life has to offer. For me, it's about taking in more data in order to build a logical system that aims to find truth and practical wisdom. I thrive the most when I am in an environment that allows me to pull together seemingly disparate ideas to create new models. In a way, I prefer to dabble in many subjects and catch a glimpse of reality through each subjects specific point of view, then afterwards draw on that repositary of perspectives to form a refined and structured model of how things really are. Exploring the endless amounts of ideas and information in the world is a fascinating pursuit for me. While exploring the endless array of possibilities is fun, I also value the importance of having a core set of beleifs and ideas- a structure or model- that guides and informs me as I navigate my way through the matrix of information. In this way, I seek to alter and refractor my base model as I gain new insights from incoming data. Primary, I focus on my cognative functions and how this affects my perception and processing of reality and my intake of external stimulus. In addition to congative processes, I have found that there are many personality assessment that assist me in accurately determining certain tendencies and responses that I have in regards to things like expectations, friends, authority and making decisions.
